{"tid":59710,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【無限金錢】超級經理人唔係講笑   中超球會24.4億斟C朗","createTime":"2016-12-30T01:00:52.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-30T05:20:43.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6ee992a073fc6984fd3722e20c0b242ea9c41704","tid":59710,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T01:00:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161230/large/1483054546_9516.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161230%2Flarge%2F1483054546_9516.jpg&h=2a465aff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中超球會無限燒錢成為今年尾最矚目轉會新聞，奧斯卡杜斯山度士、泰維斯等加盟，屢破中國球壇最高轉會費紀錄，以及成為最多人工球員。不過，根據球壇超級經理人佐治文迪斯透露，原來有中超球會打基斯坦奴朗拿度（C朗）主意，願意開價3億歐元（約24.4億港元）羅致葡萄牙隊友，確實誇得很，這個數字是目前最高轉會費紀錄保持者保羅普巴的三倍。至於朗Gor的人工，會達到每年1億歐元，冠絕全球。不過，文迪斯直言朗Gor決定留在皇家馬德里，故金錢並非萬能。"},{"pid":"ee9df003b13c833cd3840956daa1e8b7e3d51a53","tid":59710,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T01:06:16.000Z","msg":"三億歐元同等價值人仔？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b5aadcae0146411ab3c48a08d8c70d9eef41840","tid":59710,"uid":7343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T01:24:41.000Z","msg":"泰維斯周薪60萬鎊<br />\n<br />\n一星期一架超跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7b9d34e233c1ab62997cd6575197a992a5bbcf9","tid":59710,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T01:50:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>泰維斯周薪60萬鎊<br />\n<br />\n一星期一架超跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一個禮拜一層樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢地黎香港買樓可以做大地主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e56af52198dfbca41018b7b581d6c92f49ce816c","tid":59710,"uid":42396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T02:35:34.000Z","msg":"<blockq